{
  "dialogue": {
    "Ah, the new farmer we've all been expecting... and whose arrival has sparked many a conversation!": [
      "Introduction"
    ],
    "I'm Elliott... I live in the little cabin by the beach. It's a pleasure to meet you.": [
      "Introduction_sv1"
    ],
    "I'm honored that you would remember my birthday! Thank you!": [
      "AcceptBirthdayGift_Positive"
    ],
    "Another year gone by, another gray hair... I suppose this gift can commemorate my decline.": [
      "AcceptBirthdayGift_Negative"
    ],
    "Ah, what a gift! The aroma alone is inspiring...": [
      "AcceptGift_StardropTea"
    ],
    "Of course... it would be an honor! I look forward to it.": [
      "FlowerDance_Accept"
    ],
    "Ah, you've been doing some beach combing... A fine hobby! Thank you.": [
      "AcceptGift_forage_item_beach"
    ],
    "Ah, a book... Yes, perhaps the prose within these pages will offer a new insight. Thank you.": [
      "AcceptGift_book_item"
    ],
    "Ah, a bottle of fine ink. A writer can never have too much... and it's quite expensive! Thank you!": [
      "AcceptGift_814"
    ],
    "This will make a beautiful quill! I feel inspired already...": [
      "AcceptGift_444"
    ],
    "It's rare to see so many people at the beach. All for the love of squid!": [
      "SquidFest"
    ],
    "Ah... please excuse the mess in my cabin. I wasn't expecting anyone to enter!": [
      "firstVisit_ElliottHouse"
    ],
    "Agh, it's still wriggling! Get that abomination away from me!": [
      "AcceptGift_154",
      "AcceptGift_155"
    ],
    "I only wish I had given you a bouquet first!": ["dating_Elliott"],
    "%Elliott whispers a sweet secret into your ear.": [
      "dating_Elliott_memory_oneday"
    ],
    "You've plucked Pelican Town's finest flower... Now, you must care for it with all your heart.": [
      "married_Elliott"
    ],
    "Well, if it isn't the town's number one ice fisher! That was truly an impressive performance.": [
      "wonIceFishing"
    ],
    "I never stand a chance, but I always participate just to be sporting.": [
      "wonIceFishing_sv1"
    ],
    "Did you know? A duck's feather makes for an excellent quill.": [
      "purchasedAnimal_Duck"
    ],
    "You've been very helpful... Now, I must think...": ["eventSeen_39"],
    "I had a good time at the saloon the other day... Though my liver is not quite so enthusiastic...": [
      "eventSeen_40_memory_oneday"
    ],
    "That was quite the ride!": ["Resort_Entering"],
    "I'll see you back in the valley.": ["Resort_Leaving"],
    "Hopefully a crab hasn't snuck onto my clothes again.": [
      "Resort_Leaving_2"
    ],
    "Imagine crawling out of a pocket and finding yourself on a beach hundreds of miles from home!": [
      "Resort_Leaving_2_sv1"
    ],
    "Hmmm... Perhaps this could make for an interesting novel...": [
      "Resort_Leaving_2_sv2"
    ],
    "I'm just taking a quick break to slather some coconut oil on my body.": [
      "Resort_Chair"
    ],
    "Gus, I'll order a round for everyone!": ["Resort_Bar"],
    "*hic*... Oh... I don't have the G.": ["Resort_Bar_sv1"],
    "Heh heh... Never mind!": ["Resort_Bar_sv2"],
    "I've heard rumors of pirates coming to shore near here at night. They say it can get pretty wild!": [
      "Resort_Wander"
    ],
    "I must admit, this beach blows my own humble strand out of the water.": [
      "Resort"
    ],
    "Oh dear! Some seaweed has tangled itself in my hair.": ["Resort_2"],
    "That's the trouble with relaxing on the beach.": ["Resort_2_sv1"],
    "Yes... could I refuse that soft, kind face? The touch of spring-time's sweet embrace?": [
      "FlowerDance_Accept_Spouse"
    ],
    "Excuse me... not today.": ["FlowerDance_Decline"],
    "...": ["divorced"],
    "Why do you torment me? Can't you see you've shattered all my hopes and dreams?": [
      "divorced_sv1"
    ],
    "Go away. I can't bear to see you.": ["dumped_Guys"],
    "You've hurt me beyond measure... but I'm willing to leave the past behind us.": [
      "secondChance_Guys"
    ],
    "Ah... the wilted bouquet. A sight I'd hoped to never see...": ["breakUp"],
    "I suppose there are other horizons to set my eyes upon...": [
      "breakUp_sv1"
    ],
    "I'm kind of new to this town myself, but I really feel at home.": ["Mon"],
    "I moved here only a year before you.": ["Mon_sv1"],
    "I hope you've come to think of this place as 'home'.": ["Mon4"],
    "A great idea can pass through your head when you least expect it... but if your mind is too busy you might miss it.": [
      "Tue"
    ],
    "Well, I really must get back to my work.": ["Tue_sv1"],
    "The sweet friction of pen and paper is the music of my soul.": ["Tue6"],
    "That's why I chose this beach as my home, so that I could have peace and quiet to do my work.": [
      "Tue6_sv1"
    ],
    "The forest is a wonderful place. Have you been there?": ["Wed"],
    "Sorry, I'm feeling morose today.": ["Wed8"],
    "I wish there was more certainty about the future.": ["Wed8_sv1"],
    "I don't want to grow old as a lonely hermit on this beach...": [
      "Wed8_sv2"
    ],
    "I can't seem to find the inspiration to begin writing my novel...": [
      "Thu2"
    ],
    "I've been feeling hopeful lately. Perhaps the weather is changing.": [
      "Thu4"
    ],
    "Sometimes I wonder if I might just have an inflated self-image and no real skills...": [
      "Thu6"
    ],
    "No, no... I'm not fishing for compliments. Though they are appreciated...": [
      "Thu6_sv1"
    ],
    "It's a little lonely out here on the beach... so I apologize if I was ever a little too forward with you when we first met. I was just eager to have a friend.": [
      "Thu8_chance_1"
    ],
    "It feels good to have a close friend like you.": ["Thu8_chance_2"],
    "Hello, @.": ["Thu"],
    "Are you well?": ["Thu_sv1"],
    "The fresh air of this valley is good for body and mind.": ["Fri"],
    "A quick stroll outdoors always invigorates me.": ["Fri_sv1"],
    "Ah... do not get too close to my hair with a torch...": ["Fri4"],
    "I'll admit... it takes me several hours each morning to make my hair look this good.": [
      "Fri8"
    ],
    "You probably wouldn't like it inside my cabin. It's dark and full of spiders.": [
      "Sat"
    ],
    "Please excuse the sorry state of my cabin.": ["Sat4"],
    "Some people are shy. Keep showing interest in them and they'll get comfortable around you.": [
      "Sat6"
    ],
    "Everyone likes to have friends, even that grumpy blacksmith.": [
      "Sat6_sv1"
    ],
    "Hello. I hope your new farming life is panning out as you'd hoped?": [
      "Sun"
    ],
    "Oh, @! I was hoping you'd show up.": ["Sun6"],
    "It's always a pleasure to see you.": ["Sun6_sv1"],
    "Mystery, huh? It's definitely an exciting genre. I'll remember that.": [
      "event_idea1"
    ],
    "Ah, one of the classic genres. I'll remember that.": ["event_idea2"],
    "I would've never guessed! I suppose even those of the 'earthiest' profession sometimes have their heads in the stars.": [
      "event_idea3"
    ],
    "I'll remember that.": ["event_idea3_sv1"],
    "... I was worried you might not feel this way about another man.": [
      "event_boat1_male_farmer"
    ],
    "So am I.": ["event_boat1_female_farmer"],
    "Oh! I'm so sorry.%fork": ["event_boat2"],
    "Well...okay.": ["event_toast1"],
    "Here's to @!": ["event_toast1_sv1"],
    "That's a great idea!": ["event_toast2"],
    "Here's to us!": ["event_toast2_sv1"],
    "Hmmph...forget it.": ["event_toast3"],
    "Ah, to a harmonious future for the community... what a virtuous idea.": [
      "event_toast4"
    ],
    "Here's to Pelican Town!": ["event_toast4_sv1"],
    "A gentle little sunbeam woke me up this morning. I've never felt so refreshed.": [
      "summer_Mon"
    ],
    "I'm sorry if that isn't very interesting to you.": ["summer_Mon_sv1"],
    "I know that I am kind of an 'oddball'.": ["summer_Mon4"],
    "I hope you don't mind.": ["summer_Mon4_sv1"],
    "@, I know you have faith in my abilities as a writer. That means a lot to me.": [
      "summer_Mon6"
    ],
    "I've encountered some beautiful shells in front of my house.": [
      "summer_Tue"
    ],
    "I would imagine the rarer varieties to be quite valuable.": [
      "summer_Tue_sv1"
    ],
    "I write in hopes of connecting with others through time and space.": [
      "summer_Tue6"
    ],
    "*sigh*...times are changing, though. People don't read anymore.": [
      "summer_Tue6_sv1"
    ],
    "It must be satisfying to follow your crop from seed to harvest.": [
      "summer_Wed"
    ],
    "It's as if your essence is infused into the fruit.": ["summer_Wed_sv1"],
    "Oh dear! My shoes are filled with sand.": ["summer_Thu"],
    "That's the trouble with living on the beach.": [
      "summer_Thu_sv1",
      "fall_Thu_sv1"
    ],
    "@? You look puzzled.": ["summer_Fri"],
    "I guess the hot summer air can make us a little dizzy.": [
      "summer_Fri_sv1"
    ],
    "The sun is angry today... My skin is a bit too delicate, I'm afraid.": [
      "summer_Sat"
    ],
    "You came all the way here just to talk to me? How kind.": ["summer_Sun"],
    "Visit my cabin whenever you like. I could use the company.": [
      "summer_Sun4"
    ],
    "Hello @.": ["fall_Mon"],
    "Make sure and take breaks from your work now and then.": ["fall_Mon_sv1"],
    "Come visit me if you need a break from your labors.": ["fall_Mon4"],
    "I'm usually at my house.": ["fall_Mon4_sv1"],
    "It's been said that a pirate's ship, full of plundered gold, shipwrecked here a long time ago.": [
      "fall_Tue"
    ],
    "Let's not get in a tizzy, now... Gus! I propose a round of drinks to settle the nerves!%noturn": [
      "GreenRain"
    ],
    "Ah, yet another unique day in the valley. Stimulating, to say the least!": [
      "GreenRain_2"
    ],
    "@, I was just thinking about you.": ["fall_Tue8"],
    "Maybe you sensed it.": ["fall_Tue8_sv1"],
    "So! Tell me about your day.": ["fall_Tue8_sv2"],
    "I wouldn't mind trying my hand at farming.": ["fall_Wed8"],
    "The quiet atmosphere of a farm might be a good source of literary inspiration, don't you think?": [
      "fall_Wed8_sv1"
    ],
    "Oh dear! A tiny crab appears to have made his home in my shirt pocket.": [
      "fall_Thu"
    ],
    "My legs are stiff from sitting at my writing desk all night.": [
      "fall_Fri4"
    ],
    "Sometimes I envy you, @.": ["fall_Fri4_sv1"],
    "My legs are stiff from sitting at my writing desk all morning.": [
      "fall_Fri"
    ],
    "@, when you're around... I feel unusually creative.": ["fall_Fri10"],
    "I know... strange, but it's true.": ["fall_Fri10_sv1"],
    "It gets windy this time of year. Marvelous!": ["fall_Sat"],
    "I have to remember to water my plants today. And not with sea water this time!": [
      "fall_Sun"
    ],
    "You've come to visit me in the cold?": ["winter_Mon"],
    "I could do with a respite from my lonely labors.": ["winter_Mon_sv1"],
    "@, you've trudged through the snow to visit me?": ["winter_Mon4"],
    "I'm honored!": ["winter_Mon4_sv1"],
    "People have scraped a living off the sea for thousands of years.": [
      "winter_Tue"
    ],
    "I just go to the grocery store.": ["winter_Tue_sv1"],
    "@, I had a feeling that you would show up.": ["winter_Tue10"],
    "Perhaps we're connected by an other-worldly thread.": ["winter_Tue10_sv1"],
    "A day can never be boring when you follow the whims of your imagination.": [
      "-winter_Wed"
    ],
    "Sorry, am I babbling on about nonsense?": ["-winter_Wed_sv1"],
    "Breathe deeply. Do you notice it? That's the smell of the sea.": [
      "winter_Thu",
      "winter_Thu6"
    ],
    "How does it make you feel?": ["winter_Thu_sv1"],
    "Whenever I smell the sea, it reminds me of my youth. The ocean really impressed me as a child.": [
      "winter_Thu6_sv1"
    ],
    "I have to brush my hair daily, or else it'll clump up into messy knots.": [
      "winter_Fri"
    ],
    "It's a lot of work.": ["winter_Fri_sv1"],
    "I'm surprised I haven't just shaved it off in a fit of passion.": [
      "winter_Fri_sv2"
    ],
    "I suppose I am too vain.": ["winter_Fri_sv3"],
    "I've been doing little indoor exercises, since it's often too cold to go out.": [
      "winter_Sat"
    ],
    "Sorry if it's a little humid in the cabin.": ["winter_Sat_sv1"],
    "I really should scrub my floorboards today. I think an algae is starting to form.": [
      "winter_Sun"
    ],
    "Do you make time for cleaning?": ["winter_Sun_sv1"]
  },
  "marriage_dialogue": {
    "I feel inspired today... I think I'll do some writing.": ["Rainy_Day_0"],
    "The sound of rain, in some tiny way, reminds me of my cabin by the beach.": [
      "Rainy_Day_1"
    ],
    "The farm is wonderful, but I do miss the sound of the ocean.": [
      "Rainy_Day_1_sv1"
    ],
    "I got up early and made coffee.": ["Rainy_Day_2"],
    "I find that a cup of this exquisite brew makes the early morning a lot more pleasant.": [
      "Rainy_Day_2_sv1"
    ],
    "I think I'll remain indoors today, my dear. The rain causes my hair to go limp.": [
      "Rainy_Day_3"
    ],
    "My inspiration for writing is like the weather... it comes and goes at random. Today I feel entirely dull.": [
      "Rainy_Day_4"
    ],
    "Perhaps I'll read one of the classics to get my creative juices flowing.": [
      "Rainy_Day_4_sv1"
    ],
    "Ah, what a lovely day to read a book... don't you think, my dear?": [
      "patio_Elliott"
    ],
    "Good evening. Did you have a productive day, @?": [
      "Rainy_Night_0_male_farmer"
    ],
    "Good evening. Did you have a productive day, my dear?": [
      "Rainy_Night_0_female_farmer"
    ],
    "You're ice cold! Let me keep you warm.": ["Rainy_Night_1"],
    "My skill with words is unmatched, yet I can't find the way to properly describe your allure.": [
      "Rainy_Night_2_male_farmer"
    ],
    "My skill with words is unmatched, yet I can't find the way to properly describe your beauty.": [
      "Rainy_Night_2_female_farmer"
    ],
    "What did I do today? I'll just say this... it takes a lot of work to maintain this rugged physique!": [
      "Rainy_Night_3"
    ],
    "I spent the afternoon daydreaming about the ocean. So I decided to cook some seafood.": [
      "Rainy_Night_4"
    ],
    "I've been taking much better care of myself now that we're together. The bachelor life wasn't particularly healthy for me.": [
      "Indoor_Day_0"
    ],
    "Good morning, @! I made us a pot of coffee.": ["Indoor_Day_1"],
    "I find myself craving this robust flavor nearly every morning.": [
      "Indoor_Day_1_sv1"
    ],
    "If you find a spider in the house, don't squash it! Just let me know and I'll take the poor thing outside.": [
      "Indoor_Day_2"
    ],
    "Today is going to be a fantastic day... I can feel it!": ["Indoor_Day_3"],
    "I get this special feeling in my nose...": ["Indoor_Day_3_sv1"],
    "I've had this recurring nightmare that you gave me a buzz cut... You wouldn't ever do that to me, would you?": [
      "Indoor_Day_4"
    ],
    "I trust you.": ["Indoor_Day_4_sv1"],
    "From the brightest winter star, to the shimmer of an iridium vein... nothing can compare to my wonderful man.": [
      "Indoor_Night_0_male_farmer"
    ],
    "From the brightest winter star, to the fragrant fairy rose... nothing can compare with your captivating beauty.": [
      "Indoor_Night_0_female_farmer"
    ],
    "A crackling fire adds wonderful ambience to the house... every piece of wood burns in a unique way.": [
      "Indoor_Night_1"
    ],
    "I never had much success growing plant in my old beach house. Hopefully I can pick up a thing or two by watching you.": [
      "Indoor_Night_2"
    ],
    "In this respect, you are the master and I only a humble apprentice.": [
      "Indoor_Night_2_sv1"
    ],
    "When I behold thy wondrous face, a precious jewel of form and grace, my heart... torn by the dread of night, is purified with golden light.": [
      "Indoor_Night_3"
    ],
    "Poetry is the only way I can begin to describe my feelings for you.": [
      "Indoor_Night_3_sv1"
    ],
    "My love... I wouldn't trade you for 100 iridium bars.": ["Indoor_Night_4"],
    "Nor 1000...": ["Indoor_Night_4_sv1"],
    "Not even 10,000 bars, no.": ["Indoor_Night_4_sv2"],
    "...": ["Indoor_Night_4_sv3", "Indoor_Night_4_sv5"],
    "No, not even 100,000 bars!": ["Indoor_Night_4_sv4"],
    "Wa... one million bars of pure iridium...? Don't make me do this...": [
      "Indoor_Night_4_sv6"
    ],
    "My wildest dreams have come true... just look at this incredible landscape!": [
      "Outdoor_0"
    ],
    "Fertile soil beneath my feet, fresh air to fill my lungs, and the sun's warmth to delight my skin... Life is going well.": [
      "Outdoor_1"
    ],
    "I might stay here and write some poetry. I'm feeling a sudden surge of creativity! You go on ahead and take care of business.": [
      "Outdoor_2"
    ],
    "If I stay perfectly still, perhaps a resplendent butterfly will bless my nose with a landing.": [
      "Outdoor_3"
    ],
    "I drank too much coffee... my mouth feels about as dry as the Calico Desert.": [
      "Outdoor_4"
    ],
    "Oh... sorry about the coffee breath.": ["Outdoor_4_sv1"],
    "Have you had any time to entertain little %kid1 today? Maybe a second child will make things easier for both of us.": [
      "OneKid_0"
    ],
    "Little %kid1 is going to have the perfect childhood here. There's so much to explore.": [
      "OneKid_1"
    ],
    "Caring for babies isn't exactly my strong suit... but I'll do my best to be a good father.": [
      "OneKid_3"
    ],
    "I already gave %kid1 and %kid2 their food. They eat a lot for such small creatures!": [
      "TwoKids_0"
    ],
    "I was carrying %kid1 earlier, and I could've sworn I heard a \"Da...da\".": [
      "TwoKids_1"
    ],
    "I'm going to teach %kid1 to read as soon as possible! That's a great way for children to learn about the world.": [
      "TwoKids_2"
    ],
    "We've done well, @. The farm is doing excellent and our healthy children are a great joy. I couldn't be happier.": [
      "TwoKids_3"
    ],
    "@... I'm so proud of all your hard work. I'm very lucky to have you.": [
      "Good_0"
    ],
    "I made a whole secret book of poems expressing my love for you.": [
      "Good_1"
    ],
    "I came to the valley to find the ivory tower from which my talents could reign supreme. But what I really found was a dungeon of loneliness. You saved me from that.": [
      "Good_2"
    ],
    "Wow, you look really handsome today! Did you shave? Your jawline is perfect.": [
      "Good_3_male_farmer"
    ],
    "Your feminine allure is irresistible today. I can't keep my eyes off you.": [
      "Good_3_female_farmer"
    ],
    "I feel burnt out in your absence. But when I hear that sound of muddy boots on wood, my heart rises from the ash.": [
      "Good_4"
    ],
    "I'm doing a walking meditation. It's good for creativity.": ["Good_5"],
    "Be careful out there! I do worry about you sometimes. There are people in the world who would take advantage of you.": [
      "Good_6"
    ],
    "I think I'll walk down to the beach today. It's always nice to see the ocean again.": [
      "funLeave_Elliott"
    ],
    "I had a nice time at the beach by myself. I watched the waves come and go, just like old times.": [
      "funReturn_Elliott"
    ],
    "My new year's resolution is to write, write, and write! I can never stop improving my skills.": [
      "spring_1"
    ],
    "It's strange, but I often have cravings for pomegranate in the spring.": [
      "spring_12"
    ],
    "I look forward to dancing with you tomorrow, my dear.": ["spring_23"],
    "It's hard to be in a foul mood when the sun is beaming and the butterflies are dancing on a spice-berry breeze.": [
      "summer_1"
    ],
    "I was going to grab an extra bottle of ink from my cabin today, but then I remembered the Luau is tomorrow. I'll just do it then.": [
      "summer_10"
    ],
    "All good things must come to an end, including the joyful days of summer. The key to happiness is to accept change without judgment.": [
      "summer_27"
    ],
    "The splendor of fall... a verdant banquet for all the senses to enjoy... has inspired some of the greatest poetry of all time.": [
      "fall_1"
    ],
    "I might set my pride aside and sink my eager teeth into a sloppy, saucy barbecue sandwich tomorrow.": [
      "fall_15"
    ],
    "Would you still love me if I guzzled two gallons of pumpkin ale at the Spirit's Eve festival? Sometimes a man has primitive urges...": [
      "fall_26"
    ],
    "Winter is a great time to read books and play the piano. Remember to pause and enjoy a quiet moment or two.": [
      "winter_1"
    ],
    "I'm a little out of practice, but I plan on entering the fishing contest tomorrow! You've got some stiff competition, dear.": [
      "winter_7"
    ],
    "Happy new year's eve, my dear. Please accept this to celebrate.": [
      "winter_28"
    ]
  },
  "gift_tastes": {
    "Oh, this is a beautiful gift! Thank you!": ["ElliottGiftTastes_1"],
    "This is for me? Marvelous!": ["ElliottGiftTastes_2"],
    "Oh, a present! Thank you!": ["ElliottGiftTastes_3"],
    "Hmm... I'm not a huge fan of this.": ["ElliottGiftTastes_4"],
    "This item gives me a terrible feeling. I'll have to dispose of it.": [
      "ElliottGiftTastes_5"
    ]
  },
  "misc": {
    "It's nice of you to visit.": ["ElliottHouse_Elliott_Greeting1"],
    "Hello": ["ElliottHouse_Elliott_Greeting2"],
    "Hello, there!": ["ElliottHouse_Elliott_Greeting3"],
    "You're the new farmer, aren't you?": ["WipedMemory"],
    "You seem... no. I'm sure we've never met.": ["WipedMemory_sv1"],
    "This... Are you trying to hurt me even more?": ["Divorced_bouquet"],
    "I don't want your gift.": ["Divorced_gift"],
    "I foresee this to be an exquisite night!": ["Elliott_love_BeforeMovie"],
    "I feel as if my spirit is charged... as if the energy of the film was transferred to me. Incredible!": [
      "Elliott_love_AfterMovie"
    ],
    "I've avoided all information about this film... I like to go in completely 'blind'!": [
      "Elliott_like_BeforeMovie"
    ],
    "Very interesting... I'll be pondering that one for a while.": [
      "Elliott_like_AfterMovie"
    ],
    "It would be a lie to say I'm looking forward to this one...": [
      "Elliott_dislike_BeforeMovie"
    ],
    "That was very mundane, don't you think?": ["Elliott_dislike_AfterMovie"],
    "Sorry, I've already got plans to see a movie today, but maybe you can join us there?": [
      "MovieInvite_InvitedBySomeoneElse"
    ],
    "I don't feel like going to the movies again just yet...": [
      "MovieInvite_FarmerAlreadySeen"
    ],
    "Sorry, I've already seen a movie this week...": [
      "MovieInvite_AlreadySeen"
    ],
    "Sorry, I'm not in the mood to see a movie right now...": [
      "MovieInvite_Reject"
    ],
    "A movie? Sure. I'll meet you at the theater.": ["MovieInvite_Invited"],
    "A movie? Yeah, whatever, sounds good. See you at the theater...": [
      "MovieInvite_Invited_Rude"
    ],
    "Yes, my dear, I'd love to see a movie with you! I'll meet you at the theater.": [
      "MovieInvite_Spouse_Elliott"
    ],
    "Of course I'll dance with you!": ["Event_cs_1632"],
    "Okay. I look forward to it.": ["Event_cs_1633_sv1"],
    "You want to be my partner for the flower dance?": ["Event_cs_1634"],
    "Okay! I'd love to.": ["Event_cs_1634_sv1"],
    "I'm sorry... I already have a partner.": ["Event_cs_1635"],
    "...Yes, dear?": ["Event_cs_1736"],
